  {"id":"ntpc-m-0001","correctOption":"D","difficulty":"medium","sourceYear":2023,"en":{"question":"Simplify: 48 / 12 x [(9/4 of 4/3) / (3/4 of 2/3)]","options":["12","16","18","24"],"explanation":"48/12 = 4. Inside brackets: (9/4 x 4/3) = 3. (3/4 x 2/3) = 1/2. So 3 / (1/2) = 3 x 2 = 6. Final: 4 x 6 = 24."},"hi":{"question":"सरल कीजिए: 48/12 × [(4/3 का 9/4) / (2/3 का 3/4)]","options":["12","16","18","24"],"explanation":"48/12=4। कोष्ठक में: (9/4×4/3)=3, (3/4×2/3)=1/2। 3÷(1/2)=6। अंतिम: 4×6=24।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0002","correctOption":"B","difficulty":"easy","sourceYear":2024,"en":{"question":"The value of (0.5 x 0.5 + 0.3 x 0.3 + 0.2 x 0.2) / (0.5 + 0.3 + 0.2)^2 is:","options":["1","0.38","0.5","0.25"],"explanation":"Numerator = 0.25 + 0.09 + 0.04 = 0.38. Denominator = (1.0)^2 = 1. So value = 0.38."},"hi":{"question":"(0.5×0.5+0.3×0.3+0.2×0.2)/(0.5+0.3+0.2)^2 का मान क्या है?","options":["1","0.38","0.5","0.25"],"explanation":"अंश=0.25+0.09+0.04=0.38। हर=(1.0)²=1। मान=0.38।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0003","correctOption":"B","difficulty":"hard","sourceYear":2023,"en":{"question":"If x + 1/x = 4, then the value of x^4 + 1/x^4 is:","options":["196","194","192","198"],"explanation":"x^2 + 1/x^2 = (x + 1/x)^2 - 2 = 16 - 2 = 14. x^4 + 1/x^4 = (x^2 + 1/x^2)^2 - 2 = 14^2 - 2 = 196 - 2 = 194."},"hi":{"question":"यदि x+1/x=4, तो x^4+1/x^4 का मान क्या है?","options":["196","194","192","198"],"explanation":"x²+1/x²=(x+1/x)²-2=16-2=14। x⁴+1/x⁴=(x²+1/x²)²-2=196-2=194।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0004","correctOption":"B","difficulty":"medium","sourceYear":2023,"en":{"question":"Simplify: 0.4 x 0.4 x 0.4 + 0.6 x 0.6 x 0.6 / (0.4 x 0.4 - 0.4 x 0.6 + 0.6 x 0.6)","options":["0.8","1.0","1.2","0.6"],"explanation":"Using a^3 + b^3 = (a+b)(a^2-ab+b^2), where a=0.4, b=0.6. Expression = (0.4+0.6) x (a^2-ab+b^2) / (a^2-ab+b^2) = 0.4+0.6 = 1.0."},"hi":{"question":"सरल कीजिए: (0.4³+0.6³)/(0.4²-0.4×0.6+0.6²)","options":["0.8","1.0","1.2","0.6"],"explanation":"a³+b³=(a+b)(a²-ab+b²) से, व्यंजक = 0.4+0.6 = 1.0।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0005","correctOption":"B","difficulty":"hard","sourceYear":2022,"en":{"question":"What is the value of 48 / 12 x (9/8 of 4/3 / 3/4 of 2/3)?","options":["8","12","6","10"],"explanation":"First solve inner: 9/8 of 4/3 = 9/8 x 4/3 = 3/2. 3/4 of 2/3 = 3/4 x 2/3 = 1/2. (3/2)/(1/2) = 3. Then: 48/12 x 3 = 4 x 3 = 12."},"hi":{"question":"48/12 × (4/3 का 9/8 ÷ 2/3 का 3/4) का मान क्या है?","options":["8","12","6","10"],"explanation":"भीतर: 9/8×4/3=3/2, 3/4×2/3=1/2। (3/2)/(1/2)=3। फिर: 48/12×3=4×3=12।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0006","correctOption":"C","difficulty":"easy","sourceYear":2024,"en":{"question":"Simplify: 2/3 + 3/7 - 1/4.","options":["73/84","75/84","71/84","77/84"],"explanation":"LCM of 3, 7, 4 = 84. 2/3 = 56/84, 3/7 = 36/84, 1/4 = 21/84. Result = 56 + 36 - 21 = 71/84."},"hi":{"question":"सरल कीजिए: 2/3 + 3/7 - 1/4","options":["73/84","75/84","71/84","77/84"],"explanation":"ल.स.(3,7,4)=84। 2/3=56/84, 3/7=36/84, 1/4=21/84। 56+36-21=71/84।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0007","correctOption":"A","difficulty":"easy","sourceYear":2024,"en":{"question":"What is the value of square root of 0.000144?","options":["0.012","0.12","0.0012","0.00012"],"explanation":"sqrt(0.000144) = sqrt(144/1000000) = 12/1000 = 0.012."},"hi":{"question":"0.000144 का वर्गमूल क्या है?","options":["0.012","0.12","0.0012","0.00012"],"explanation":"√(0.000144)=√(144/1000000)=12/1000=0.012।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0008","correctOption":"A","difficulty":"medium","sourceYear":2023,"en":{"question":"Find the value of: (4.5)^2 - (2.5)^2 / (4.5 - 2.5)","options":["7","6","5","8"],"explanation":"Using a^2 - b^2 = (a-b)(a+b). Expression = (4.5-2.5)(4.5+2.5)/(4.5-2.5) = 4.5+2.5 = 7."},"hi":{"question":"(4.5²-2.5²)/(4.5-2.5) का मान ज्ञात कीजिए।","options":["7","6","5","8"],"explanation":"a²-b²=(a-b)(a+b) से, व्यंजक=(4.5+2.5)=7।"}}
